data.description: This charming 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath home offers a warm and inviting space to call your own. Conveniently located near expressways and schools, it blends convenience with tranquility. Enjoy the open floor plan that seamlessly connects the living spaces. The kitchen is spacious and designed so you can prepare favorite meals while remaining a part of the action and share in the memories with the rest of the home. Upstairs features a laundry space and a bedroom with a vaulted ceiling. The oversized primary bedroom connects to a generously sized bathroom and boasts a spacious walk-in closet. The basement showcases tall ceilings to create an expansive and versatile blank canvas awaiting your personal touch. A finished full bath in the basement adds to the appeal. Call for your showing today!
